ğŸ§  BST vs Binary Tree:

| Feature          | Binary Tree             | BST                             |
|------------------|--------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Structure        | Any                     | Ordered                         |
| Left/Right Rule  | No rule                 | Left < Root < Right             |
| Inorder Sorted   | Not always              | Always (ascending)              |
| Search Efficiency| Poor (O(N))             | Good (O(log N) average case)    |

