ğŸ”¹ Inorder traversal = Sorted order
ğŸ”¹ No duplicate values (in most implementations)
ğŸ”¹ Fast insert/search/delete when tree is balanced
ğŸ”¹ Left subtree < Node < Right subtree
ğŸ”¹ For recursion: Pass valid lower and upper bounds
ğŸ”¹ Worst case: Skewed tree â†’ O(N) time

